I was called and I came. What's up?

1524
01:43:12,475 --> 01:43:14,556
HONEY:William's just turned down Anna Scott.

1525
01:43:16,116 --> 01:43:18,916
SPIKE:You daft prick.

1526
01:43:18,956 --> 01:43:22,236
No, no.
No, no, it's actually quite sensible.

1527
01:43:25,436 --> 01:43:29,036
BELLA:That painting
isn't the original, is it?

1528
01:43:29,116 --> 01:43:31,596
WILLIAM:Um, you know,
I think it might be, yeah.

1529
01:43:34,396 --> 01:43:36,676
