she wanted to go out with you.

1530
01:43:39,116 --> 01:43:41,916
WILLIAM:- Yeah.
BERNIE:- Well, that's nice.

1531
01:43:43,437 --> 01:43:46,397
WILLIAM:What?

1532
01:43:46,477 --> 01:43:48,517
BERNIE:Well, you know,

1533
01:43:48,597 --> 01:43:52,557
BERNIE:anyone saying they wanna go out with you
is pretty great, isn't it?

1534
01:43:58,117 --> 01:44:00,677
WILLIAM:It was...

1535
01:44:00,757 --> 01:44:02,957
WILLIAM:sort of... sweet, actually.

1536
01:44:02,997 --> 01:44:05,837
WILLIAM:Um, I mean,
I know she's an actress and all that...

1537
01:44:05,877 --> 01:44:11,558
WILLIAM:so she can... deliver a line, but, um,

1538
01:44:11,598 --> 01:44:14,038
WILLIAM:she said she might be
as famous as she can be,

1539
01:44:14,118 --> 01:44:16,878
WILLIAM:but also that she was...

1540
01:44:16,918 --> 01:44:20,118
WILLIAM:just a girl...

1541
01:44:20,198 --> 01:44:24,398
WILLIAM:standing in front of a boy...

1542
01:44:24,438 --> 01:44:26,798
WILLIAM:asking him... to love her.

1543
01:44:41,319 --> 01:44:44,599
WILLIAM:Oh, sod a dog. I've made
the wrong decision, haven't I?

1544
01:44:46,559 --> 01:44:48,359
Yeah.

1545
01:44:48,399 --> 01:44:51,239
WILLIAM:Max, how fast is your car?

1546
01:44:51,559 --> 01:44:54,719
- # Hey #

1547
01:44:54,799 --> 01:44:58,439
MAX:- Good luck!
- If anyone gets in our way,
we have small nuclear devices.

1548
01:44:58,479 --> 01:45:00,279
- Where to?
BERNIE:- All I can think is The Ritz.

1549
01:45:00,359 --> 01:45:02,839
MAX:- Where's Bella?
HONEY:- She's not coming.

1550
01:45:02,919 --> 01:45:05,959
MAX:- Oh, sod that. Bernie, in the back.
- What?

1552
01:45:08,480 --> 01:45:10,800
- Max, I'm okay.

1553
01:45:10,880 --> 01:45:12,880
